content: I've un-nominated #88576 now that the fix has been been merged and accepted for backport. And i've marked #90940 as P-medium, and am now reviewing the fix for it. With that, the @T-libs agenda is completely empty. So let's skip that meeting and spend some time on reviewing etc.

For @T-libs-api: I've unnominated #81106, since the FCP was already started. I've started the FCP on #90896. rfc 3192 is still in active discussion. and rfc 3184 was discussed last time. And with that there's only #90830 left, which we can discuss asynchronously on the issue, or next meeting. So let's skip today's API meeting as well, and take that time to instead handle our many open FCP checkboxes: https://rfcbot.rs/
